# gctl frontend environment
#
# The Vite SPA has no required browser-exposed environment variables for the
# submission demo. It calls same-origin `/api/*` routes in Vercel production and
# uses explicit fallback envelopes during local Vite-only development.
#
# Add optional browser-safe values here only with the `VITE_` prefix.
# Never place private keys, API keys, JWTs, tokens, or server-only endpoints in
# this file; those belong in root `.env`, `.env.local`, or Vercel project env.
